SUMMARY:Deadline: Omidyar Network: Tech Journalism Fund
DESCRIPTION:The Omidyar Network Tech Journalism Fund offers rolling grants 
 of $5\,000-$25\,000 for technology journalism projects. Relevant for journ
 alists and media organizations investigating AI\, tech policy\, and AI's i
 mpacts on culture\, society\, and creative industries. Applications are ac
 cepted on a rolling basis through December 31\, 2026 — one of the few cu
 rrently open opportunities with a confirmed near-term deadline. Apply via 
 the application form on omidyar.com.\n\nOrganisation: Omidyar Network\nLoc
 ation: Open to journalists and media organizations worldwide.\nAward: $5\,
 000-$25\,000 per project. Rolling deadline through December 31\, 2026. No 
 application fee.\nDuration: Per-project\; scope and timeline defined in th
 e proposal.\n\nMore: https://omidyar.com/tech-journalism-fund-application/
URL:https://omidyar.com/tech-journalism-fund-application/
LOCATION:Open to journalists and media organizations worldwide.
